# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Stray log files — never commit by accident
# Covers publish logs, MSBuild logs, test-harness logs, ad-hoc diagnostics.
# If you ever need to commit a specific log deliberately, use
# `git add -f path/to/file.log`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log


